    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 99.</p><p>Heroic Perk: Death Mark</p><p>Prerequisite: Phantom Strike</p><p>You can use a bonus action to Death Mark a creature you can see within 60 feet. While Death Marked, you always know the creature’s exact location regardless of distance, even across planes of existence. Your attacks against a Death Marked creature ignore damage resistances, and the creature cannot benefit from invisibility or concealment against you. A Death Mark lasts until the creature dies, you mark a new target, or the creature is targeted by a remove curse spell or similar magic.</p></div>",
